title: Looking To Move Immediately? You'll Love this 2x2 Lake View!
posting_body: ['Welcome home to Sailhouse', 'Welcome home to Sailhouse Apartments!', 'Come join a Kirkland community devoted to nurturing your love of nature while simultaneously providing a remarkable array of metropolitan conveniences.', 'Our spacious and pet-friendly studio, one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans feature modern design elements and amenities.', 'Marvel at the sandy beach, boardwalk trails, fine dining, shopping, and nightlife options…all steps from your apartment!', 'Sailhouse represents the ideal backdrop for your life.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 103', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1123 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Dishwasher', '- Vaulted Ceilings', '- Granite Counter Tops', '- Walk-In Closets', '- Refrigerator with Ice Maker', '- Oven', '- Microwave', '- Washer/Dryer', '- Ceiling Fan', 'Community Amenities', '- Bike Storage', '- Additional Storage', '- Clubhouse with WiFi', '- Fitness Center', '- Pet Stations', '- BBQ/Picnic Area', '- Kayak/Paddleboard/Bike Rentals', 'Pet Policy', 'Contact Leasing Agent', 'Office Hours', 'Wednesday & Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Tuesday & Thursday 10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday & Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Sailhouse', '9740 NE 119th Way, Kirkland, WA, 98034', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', '4b77nu51OnMH']
